<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>ElectionBuddy Result Center - Coding Challenge</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>

    <%= favicon_link_tag asset_path("logo.png"), type: "image/png" %>

    <style>
      /* ElectionBuddy Welcome Page Styles */
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(0, 38, 58) 0%, rgb(0, 48, 73) 50%, #1a202c 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
        position: relative;
      }

      .bg-pattern {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        opacity: 0.1;
        background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 80%, rgba(255, 128, 2, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
                          radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(255, 128, 2, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .logo-container {
        position: fixed;
        top: 2rem;
        left: 2rem;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 100%;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        z-index: 100;
      }

      .logo-container img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        max-height: 46px;
      }

      .welcome-title {
        color: white;
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .welcome-subtitle {
        color: #FF8002;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .main-content {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
      }

      .challenge-info {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
      }

      .challenge-info h2 {
        color: rgb(0, 38, 58);
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .challenge-info p {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .code-snippets-section {
        background: #f8f9fa;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border-left: 5px solid #FF8002;
      }

      .code-snippets-section h3 {
        color: rgb(0, 38, 58);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .code-icon {
        background: #FF8002;
        color: white;
        padding: 0.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .code-placeholder {
        background: #e9ecef;
        border: 2px dashed #FF8002;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
        font-style: italic;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .code-snippets {
        text-align: left;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      .code-block {
        background: #2d3748;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        overflow-x: auto;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .code-block pre {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 1rem;
        font-family: 'Monaco', 'Menlo', 'Ubuntu Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .code-block code {
        color: #e2e8f0;
        background: transparent;
        padding: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
      }

      .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .feature-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-top: 4px solid #FF8002;
      }

      .feature-card h4 {
        color: rgb(0, 38, 58);
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      .feature-card p {
        color: #333;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding: 1rem;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #FF8002;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .footer a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .welcome-title {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .welcome-subtitle {
          font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .main-content {
          padding: 2rem;
        }

        .features-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .logo-container {
          top: 1rem;
          left: 1rem;
          width: 100px;
          height: 70px;
        }

        .logo-container img {
          max-height: 50px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="bg-pattern"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <%= image_tag "logo.png", alt: "ElectionBuddy Logo" %>
        </div>
        <h1 class="welcome-title">ElectionBuddy Result Center</h1>
        <p class="welcome-subtitle">Build the future of election results visualization</p>
      </header>

      <main class="main-content">
        <div class="challenge-info">
          <h2>üèÜ Your Mission: Build a Result Center</h2>
          <p>
            Create a modern, real-time election results dashboard that displays live vote counts,
            candidate standings, and interactive visualizations. This is your chance to showcase
            your full-stack development skills with Rails, real-time updates, and data visualization.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="code-snippets-section">
          <h3>
            <span class="code-icon">‚ö°</span>
            Database Schema Setup
          </h3>
          <div class="code-snippets">
            <h4 style="color: rgb(0, 38, 58); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Generate your Result Center models with these commands:</h4>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>rails generate model Election title:string status:string starts_at:datetime ends_at:datetime</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>rails generate model Question election:references prompt:string question_type:string position:integer</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>rails generate model Answer question:references text:string position:integer</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>rails generate model Voter election:references email:string name:string access_token:string:uniq ballot_cast_at:datetime</code></pre>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>rails generate model Ballot voter:references tally_payload:jsonb</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="code-snippets-section">
          <h3>
            <span class="code-icon">üìä</span>
            API Response Format
          </h3>
          <div class="code-snippets">
            <h4 style="color: rgb(0, 38, 58); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Expected JSON Response Format:</h4>
            <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">Example JSON Response (GET /results/:election_id)</p>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>{
  "election_id": 42,
  "questions": [
    {
      "id": 7,
      "prompt": "Who should be chair?",
      "totals": { "31": 6, "32": 4 },
      "percentages": { "31": 0.6, "32": 0.4 },
      "winner_ids": ["31"]
    }
  ]
}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="code-snippets-section">
          <h3>
            <span class="code-icon">üó≥Ô∏è</span>
            Ballot Data Structure
          </h3>
          <div class="code-snippets">
            <h4 style="color: rgb(0, 38, 58); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Suggested format for Ballot#tally_payload:</h4>
            <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">JSON structure for storing individual ballot responses</p>
            <div class="code-block">
              <pre><code>{
  "choices": {
    "q_101": 17,
    "q_102": 22
  },
  "submitted_at": "2025-07-16T19:32:40Z"
}</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>üï∞Ô∏è Real-time Analytics</h4>
            <p>Build dashboards that update live as votes are cast, showing dynamic charts and real-time statistics.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>üéØ Result Visualization</h4>
            <p>Create compelling data visualizations using modern charting libraries and interactive elements.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="feature-card">
            <h4>‚ö° Performance Focused</h4>
            <p>Optimize for high-traffic scenarios with efficient database queries and caching strategies.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>

      <footer class="footer">
        <p>
          üöÄ Built for the ElectionBuddy Result Center Challenge |
          <a href="https://electionbuddy.com" target="_blank">Discover ElectionBuddy</a>
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
